Do you guys think this build would work since it combines the cdr with shit tonnes of mana and lifesteal/spell vamp?
Build:
{{summoner:4}}  {{summoner:14}} 
RoA - Rush {{item:3027}} 
Boots of Ionity  {{item:1331}} 
Seraph&#039;s Embrace {{item:3048}} 
Lich bane {{item:3100}} 
Hex Tech Gun Blade {{item:3146}} 
and Rabadon&#039;s {{item:3089}} 

Would this work? I understand there is practically no protection and you would require some decent tanks within game but considering Kassadin&#039;s mobility and cdr potential it could be a possiblity???
